# Section 1 — Payment Flow Architecture
# Estimated time: 2 hours
# Checkpoint: answer 2 questions before moving on

Teach me:
- What actually happens between "user clicks pay" and
  "money lands in the company account" — every step
- The difference between a payment gateway, payment
  processor, and merchant account
- What a webhook is and why it is more important than
  the frontend response
- Why I should NEVER confirm a payment from the
  frontend alone
- Draw me the full payment flow as a numbered step-by-step
  list mapped to MY app:
  patient fills form → selects payment method → booking
  created → redirected to Pesapal → pays via Mobile Money
  → company gets notified → booking confirmed

